latestIgtvVideos.title: Why not CrossFit? It’s not as difficult as it appears 🙌🏼
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I have been waiting to share this really exciting CrossFit session I did with @303crossfitdrive which turned out to be rather motivating thanks to my cross fit coach @neha_agarwalla2 
My whole idea behind doing this collaboration was:
1 - Of course because I was quite excited to give Crossfit a shot, and
2 - To break the common mindset against women training hard especially when it comes to lifting heavy weights. It’s not as scary or not doable as it might appear. 
In fact, in my experience, you’ll only find it difficult until you try it & until you don’t try it, you’ll never know ⚡️ Wardrobe Courtesy: Top to bottom in  @reebokindia

Video Courtesy: @Rishav_jainphotography
